PersonalizedRecommendationSystem : Movie

3 Types of Recommendation :
Content Based
Collaborative filtering Bases
Hybrid Based

This project is Content Based

Collecting Data set -> preprocessing -> creating model -> create webapp

EDA - Exploratory data analysis

Dataset -> https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/tmdb/tmdb-movie-metadata

EDA process:
Load data set in jupyter note book
changing data type of some columns like overview , cast , crew , keyword
Removing unwanted columns and removing unwanted values
checking null values and duplicate
merge some columns and convert to paragraph
getting final data frame
Tag field convert to Count Vectorizer
creating a recommended function using a title col and list top five recommeded similar movies
save data in pickle formate
creating a streamlit app for user interface and search a movie title and listing a recommened movies for the user.

